# Agent orchestration

Roles: `.ai/agents/*.md` (orchestrator, architect, developer, test-engineer, reviewer, security-reviewer, documentation-agent, knowledge-agent, incident-agent).

For medium/high complexity:
1. Implementer pass
2. Adversarial review pass (independent of implementer claims)
3. Test-coverage pass
4. Orchestrator compares outcomes

Single-agent sessions should still simulate these passes mentally and record gaps.
